51-44-33-59 Work experience with Strategic Systems Program (SSP). For the ND-3 (intermediate) level: A bachelors degree as described above and one year of specialized professional engineering experience is required. Candidate should have experience in performing hazard analysis (i.e. preliminary, system, sub-system) on software, hardware, design, change proposals, fuzes.
